<item>
            <title>[MNG-229] plugin repository separation mixup</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-229</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;currently, dependences of plugins are resolved from the list of plugin repositories. This is most likely incorrect, and only works because it happens to be the same.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
